Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:57.54,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}君となら行けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:05:02.93,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}感じるままに伝えたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:14.70,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}いつでも　答えならtruth
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:55.90,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}相逢總是驚喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:08.70,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}「你看吧」你微笑著說  聲音像是銀鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:14.05,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}開始幾乎令人目眩  突如其來的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:19.48,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}已經不用說明來指引  只須不可思議的引力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:25.44,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}兩對眼眸就會互相吸引  心中早已沒有重力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.52,0:04:30.23,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}如果  我現在觸碰你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:33.94,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}就能聽到心扉打開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:41.20,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}命運早已無法忍耐  催我趕快行動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:47.03,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}展翅高飛  直到那堅毅夢想的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:52.57,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}將所有的密碼盡數破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:57.54,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}與你一起  定能去到前人未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:05:02.93,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}只想把最真切的感受告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:14.70,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}無論何時  我的回答都是truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.02,0:23:47.87,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}風を泳ぐ鳥の羽音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:52.56,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}真似て跳ねた朝の舗道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.83,0:23:57.61,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君の瞳　映る世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.32,0:24:02.14,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}昨日までとなにか違う
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.74,0:24:08.25,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}どんな涙も光に変わるの
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.66,0:24:14.81,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}きっと二人が出逢えた秘密がある
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.66,0:24:17.90,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Smile on me　きらりと
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.05,0:24:20.32,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Smile on you　突然
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.67,0:24:22.81,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}なんだっていまから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.06,0:24:25.16,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}できちゃいそうね
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.45,0:24:27.74,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Shine on me　かならず
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.97,0:24:30.17,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Shine on you　信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.43,0:24:32.67,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ほんとうの未来が
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.83,0:24:35.00,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そばにあること
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.69,0:24:40.37,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Pleasure treasure　この手で
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.37,0:24:40.37,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}(すぐに)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.64,0:24:45.47,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Pleasure treasure　抱きしめよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.02,0:23:47.87,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}像鳥兒振翅飛翔在風中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:52.56,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你蹦跳在晨間的人行道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.83,0:23:57.61,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你的眼眸中映出的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.32,0:24:02.14,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}與昨天似乎已有所不同
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.74,0:24:08.25,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}所有的淚  最終都會變成光
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.66,0:24:14.81,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}二人之間  又有了新的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.66,0:24:17.90,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Smile on me  一閃而過
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.05,0:24:20.32,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Smile on you  突然之間
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.67,0:24:22.81,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}總覺得有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.06,0:24:25.16,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就要從現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.45,0:24:27.74,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Shine on me  請你一定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.97,0:24:30.17,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Shine on you  要相信
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.43,0:24:32.67,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}真正的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.83,0:24:35.00,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就在你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.69,0:24:40.37,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Pleasure treasure  用你的雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.37,0:24:40.37,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}(現在)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.64,0:24:45.47,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Pleasure treasure  就去抓住它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見  齊格
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用兜帽遮得那麼嚴實  不影響看比賽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡引人注目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.73,0:00:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且又在吃這種垃圾食品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是偶爾一次啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.49,0:00:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在預選賽之前跟你見面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.50,0:00:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年感覺如何？能戰鬥到最後嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.67,0:00:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:01:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在跟維多碰面之前就缺賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.85,0:01:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事就不要再提了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.85,0:01:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你今年有精神能參加比賽就好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是我的目標啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前就說過  我可不是應該當作目標的選手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多你和老大都比我厲害得多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.26,0:01:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此我也喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.48,0:01:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡你的戰技和強大之處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.99,0:01:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有你溫柔的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.71,0:01:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看了選拔賽吧？今年的選手感覺如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.92,0:01:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有幾個孩子很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.53,0:01:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庸才不良少女  你怎麼來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是怪胎大小姐嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.18,0:01:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要從選拔賽開始打起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是  我可是6組的種子選手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:02:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也不怎麼關心你的事情  可能看漏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是  今年要是能在地區選拔賽落選就幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.74,0:02:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆直接輸掉吧  跟你戰鬥太麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.17,0:02:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多和老大都…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多次參加城市正賽的頂尖選手居然在場外吵架
